div.p: c outb(PIC1_CMD, 0x11); // ICW1: init outb(PIC2_CMD, 0x11); outb(PIC1_DATA, 32); // ICW2: master offset outb(PIC2_DATA, 40); // ICW2: slave offset outb(PIC1_DATA, 0x04); // ICW3: slave at IRQ2 outb(PIC2_DATA, 0x02); // ICW3: slave ID outb(PIC1_DATA, 0x01); // ICW4: 8086 mode outb(PIC2_DATA, 0x01);

p.strong: Vectors 8-15 are RESERVED for CPU exceptions!
